Package: birt
Title: Bayesian Rasch Models via CmdStan
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Nduka", "Boika", email = "Boikanduka@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Fit Bayesian dichotomous Rasch models using CmdStan via the 
    cmdstanr interface. Provides functions for model fitting, item and person 
    parameter estimation, model diagnostics (outfit/infit), and visualizations 
    including item characteristic curves, Wright maps, and test information 
    functions.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/ndukaboika/birt
BugReports: https://github.com/Ndukaboika/birt/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
